limit_description: Maximum number of users you want in your voice channel
permit_description: User you want to allow access to
reject_description: User you want to reject from joining your voice channel
transfer_description: User you want to transfer ownership to
invite_description: User you want to invite to your voice channel
bitrate_description: Bitrate you want to set for your voice channel
trust_description: User you would like to also manage your voice channel
untrust_description: User you would like to remove from managing your voice channel
